  "detailed_description": "Hero Express is an atypical driving game. You won't be competing with other drivers to see who reaches the goal first, you will try hard to reach the goal ALIVE. <br>Each track is filled with obstacles and hazards, and the player is the one that'll have to exploit his skill in this 2d physics-driven driving game.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/dc254625be54baa91a0d1905669ea87b.poster.avif?t=1737107444\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/dc254625be54baa91a0d1905669ea87b.webm?t=1737107444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/dc254625be54baa91a0d1905669ea87b.mp4?t=1737107444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 11 Crazy Tracks<br></li><li> 11 Unique Vehicles<br></li><li> 4 Upgradable Stats<br></li><li> 16 Different Hazards<br></li><li> 2 Powerups<br></li><li> 2 Difficulties</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/aa1b94fcdb16a323ec98e5ecb8236241.avif?t=1737107444\" width=630 height=150 /></span><br><br><br><i>Hero is really absent-minded and always forgets his heroic tools. <br>Who will save the day when the hero needs saving? The Hero Express of course. <br>And you are the best of the best, Delivery guy, the one sent on impossible missions. <br>Help Hero save the world with your mad driving skills!</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/487c3cbf6f66df3d62ecd03b4a69e2c1.avif?t=1737107444\" width=630 height=236 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Hero Express is an atypical driving game. You won't be competing with other drivers to see who reaches the goal first, you will try hard to reach the goal ALIVE. <br>Each track is filled with obstacles and hazards, and the player is the one that'll have to exploit his skill in this 2d physics-driven driving game.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/dc254625be54baa91a0d1905669ea87b.poster.avif?t=1737107444\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/dc254625be54baa91a0d1905669ea87b.webm?t=1737107444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/dc254625be54baa91a0d1905669ea87b.mp4?t=1737107444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 11 Crazy Tracks<br></li><li> 11 Unique Vehicles<br></li><li> 4 Upgradable Stats<br></li><li> 16 Different Hazards<br></li><li> 2 Powerups<br></li><li> 2 Difficulties</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/aa1b94fcdb16a323ec98e5ecb8236241.avif?t=1737107444\" width=630 height=150 /></span><br><br><br><i>Hero is really absent-minded and always forgets his heroic tools. <br>Who will save the day when the hero needs saving? The Hero Express of course. <br>And you are the best of the best, Delivery guy, the one sent on impossible missions. <br>Help Hero save the world with your mad driving skills!</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080630/extras/487c3cbf6f66df3d62ecd03b4a69e2c1.avif?t=1737107444\" width=630 height=236 /></span>",
